<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13067876/ski_onboarding_citytosnow.jpg" alt="Escape the City for the Snow" data-udi="umb://media/adf7d84ebe634a88aa50e8fcd62c7661" /></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">Thank you for taking part in our New Heights competition run in partnership with SWISS International Airlines and Swiss Travel Systems.</span></p>
<p><span>As a competition entrant, you are entitled to £25 per person off an Inghams ski holiday in Winter 2018/2019. Simply phone our call centre to book, quoting the voucher code we sent to you by email.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>Save £25 per person on a Winter 2018/2019 ski holiday</strong></span><br /></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Save £25 per person, up to a maximum of 4 people, on any Winter 2018/2019 ski holiday</span></li>
<li><span>Choose from any of our 91 ski resorts across 8 countries</span></li>
<li><span>Combinable with any other valid offer</span></li>
<li><span>Book before the 31 August 2018</span></li>
</ul>
<div class="data-grid">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 350px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
