<td align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #ff9900; border-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px; height: 18.5313px;"><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" data-udi="umb://document/6572cca460304ccea08f6a4743bbc708" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6572cca460304ccea08f6a4743bbc708}" title="Ski Late Deals">Find your next ski holiday</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
