</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="geolocation-title">Phone <strong>01483 79 11 11</strong> to book your ski holiday with your voucher.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Ski holidays to Switzerland</h2>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/umbraco/nothing.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/280be607d0364b0fafa7724102d348b8" /><img src="/media/13067881/reach-for-new-heights-winter-1819-switzerland.jpg" alt="Ski in Switzerland" data-udi="umb://media/280be607d0364b0fafa7724102d348b8" /></p>
<p>Switzerland is home to picturesque mountain villages, stunning ski runs, and fantastic hotels and restaurant with world-class hospitality. It is home to iconic ski resorts such as <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz"><strong>St Moritz</strong></a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4}" title="Verbier"><strong>Verbier</strong></a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt"><strong>Zermatt </strong></a>- destinations which have defined the modern ski holiday tradition, as well as beautiful villages like <a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen"><strong>Wengen</strong> </a>and <a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee"><strong>Saas-Fee</strong></a> that can only be accessed by train.</p>
<div class="data-grid">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 350px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 18.5313px;">
<td align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #ff9900; border-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px; height: 18.5313px;"><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Swiss ski holidays</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Winter 2018/2019</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13066457/reach-for-new-heights-winter-1819.jpg" alt="Winter 2018/2019" data-udi="umb://media/9a1e0d5fd9e4416b9a316b0e70cd0e56" /></p>
<p>At Inghams we're always excited about winter - but we're really looking forward to <a data-udi="umb://document/e4fa2ba0a37140bd9359c0faad0e95ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4fa2ba0a37140bd9359c0faad0e95ac}" title="Winter 2018/2019"><strong>Winter 2018/2019</strong></a>. Last winter gave us some of the best snow fall in a generation, re-igniting everyone's passion and interest in skiing and snowboarding. We're hoping for even more snow and even more adventures next winter. We can't wait to get back into our bindings.</p>
