</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<p style="text-align: center;">Terms and Conditions</p>
<ul>
<li>The promoter of this offer is: Inghams (Company No. 350786) whose registered office address is Mountain House, Station Road, Godalming, Surrey, GU7 1EX.</li>
<li>This offer is exclusive to accepted entrants of our Inghams New Heights Win a Break to Switzerland competition, whose entries complied with the conditions of that competition.</li>
<li>Vouchers will be issued to the entrant to the value of £25 per person, to a maximum of 4 people.</li>
<li>Vouchers may be redeemed on the value of a booking for the Winter 2018/19 season only, and must be redeemed by 31 August 2018.</li>
<li>The voucher can be applied alongside any other valid Inghams offer available at the time the booking is confirmed.</li>
<li>Discounts will be applied to confirmed bookings only, and cannot be deducted from deposit payments.</li>
<li>The voucher code will be provided by email and must be quoted at the time of making your booking, which must be by telephone with our Reservations team. Online bookings will not be accepted.</li>
<li>No cash alternative will be offered.</li>
<li>Bookings made after 31 August 2018 will not be eligible for the voucher to be applied.</li>
<li>The booking conditions and other items forming part of the holiday contract apply at all times and guests are required to read and accept these prior to making a booking with us.</li>
</ul>
